{"tid":1454379,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機場戰線 幾個方法保障自己","createTime":"2019-08-12T07:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T07:56:10.000Z","uid":225318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a881256c392208c78a15f1c7e8f292c80bc1d7c0","tid":1454379,"uid":225318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tUR0S20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtUR0S20.png&h=e0460d17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經有圖影到警犬帶旗入去，唔排除佢地選擇濫炒，係機場開槍同催淚彈。<br />\n再唔係佢地可以直接進行拘捕，因為已經好多巴士唔停T1,的士都開始避接機場單。<br />\n<br />\n係現場既大家有幾樣野要做<br />\n<br />\n1. 起碼4個人一組(最好6個)，確保有黑警扮示威者衝過黎拘捕時有足夠人力去救人。 如果佢地無辦法出催淚彈，佢地好大機會就係混入示威者中突襲拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n2. 記好警員條例，便衣人員進行拘捕時如果無出示委任證，佢無權拉你，你有權用適當武力拒捕。 <br />\n<br />\n3. 提早反擊， 現場影到咁多耳機落單狗， 6人組隊先行帶佢地入廁所。或者各種形式，𥄫住所有耳機狗，有咩動靜即刻包圍番佢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好落單啊，一定要四人以上一齊，要救人啊！</span>"},{"pid":"cea9c2da51c634315c70bdab3923c9db35dd312b","tid":1454379,"uid":225318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:11:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推 保護自己 大家加油！</span>"},{"pid":"ac6308653867d7f736d5bf3f733c30b87448a28c","tid":1454379,"uid":225318,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LiRZNn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6LiRZNn.png&h=b42ed575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小心班犬突然撲向人！"},{"pid":"d8ae3b9a37e4b890a93bfd4da6adf777a8863486","tid":1454379,"uid":225318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推 啲落單狗你地點處置都唔割</span>"},{"pid":"e64c920ab529397f66af4322b80fbd27c3c7ed04","tid":1454379,"uid":225318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"cx source <br />\nAA sent message to all airline management.<br />\n今天餘下所有航班取消<br />\n已從外站起飛嘅航班有機會未能於香港國際機場降落<br />\n而未起飛嘅亦唔會俾clearance走"},{"pid":"543f23b3242d4ca502189a41636468c2a2e3459a","tid":1454379,"uid":225318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:54:40.000Z","msg":"小心啲狗困獸鬥<br />\n有必要時買定機票保平安"},{"pid":"3e2ffafe4897a567151155580179ce9223197e05","tid":1454379,"uid":225318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:56:10.000Z","msg":"或者T2 IMAX 買張戲飛 <br />\n<br />\n4人以上一隊 救手足"}]}